* Identify\nFailure Cause
** Navigation
***_ Jobs & Pipelines
***_ Select job name
***_ Runs tab
** Matrix View
***_ Visual run history
***_ Cells = task status
***_ Red = failed task
** Investigation Steps
***_ Hover failed task
***_ See start/end/duration
***_ Read error messages
***_ Open Task run details
** Pattern Analysis
***_ Repeated same task = code issue
***_ Random failures = cluster issue
** Diagnose Error
***_ Databricks Assistant
***_ Analyzes error messages
***_ Suggests fixes
@endmindmap
